													<div id="info-fragment-0"class="info ">  
							<h2><a href="#">Welcome to the Hamilton Campus</a></h2>  
							<p>Featuring: Teacher Education, IRC, Computer Labs and SMART Room</p>
							</div>  
														<!-- First Content -->  
							<div id="fragment-0" class="ui-tabs-panel ">
							<img src="/sites/default/files/P1030125_1.JPG" alt="outside view of the hamilton campus" />							</div>
												</div>
					  
					<div id="pagehdr">
																													</div><!-- END PAGEHDR -->
					      <div id="horizon-feature">
              </div>
    <!-- BEGIN OUTER-LEFT -->
<div id="outer-left">
        <div id="node-19788" class="node clear-block">
        <div class="content">
 	    <h3 class="pgtitle">Hamilton Campus</h3> 
        <span class='print-link'></span><p><span lang="EN" style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN">Brock University officially opened the Hamilton campus in 2000. The </span><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">primary user of this facility is the Faculty of Education&rsquo;s Department of Teacher Education. Other departments who utilize the facility on a regular basis are Graduate Studies in Education and Department of Continuing Teacher Education.</span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm;tab-stops:list 36.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">The Department of Teacher Education offers the following programs:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;<br />
mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">Primary/Junior</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;<br />
mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">Junior/Intermediate </span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;<br />
mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">Intermediate/Senior </span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;<br />
mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">Technological Education - expected January 2017.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-indent:0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;<br />
mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">For general enquiries about the Hamilton Campus please contact reception at 905 547 3555 x3610. </span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN" style="font-family:<br />
&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN">The Hamilton campus also offers students the use of an Instructional Resource Centre (IRC) which provides specialized instructional resources (kits, puppets, teacher guides, etc.) required to support Faculty of Education Programs. The IRC also provides media services and one-stop audio-visual services for instructors and teacher candidates (e.g. LCD projectors and document cameras are available for use during teaching practicums). Media production facilities, instructional supply sales, and technical assistance are also available through the IRC.</span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:<br />
&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">The campus supports two Windows-based computer labs, houses a number of SMART boards, classroom audio systems, and other educational technologies to support 21<sup>st</sup> century teaching and learning. Wireless networking is available throughout the building and requires a Brock login in order to connect. For additional information on the computer labs or specific questions about the technology resources available at the Hamilton campus, please contact Kyle Tuck, Systems Administrator and Technician at x3606.</span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm;tab-stops:list 36.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">Available to the public, is the rental of the Hamilton campus facility, namely the gymnasium and classrooms. These are typically booked for special events, ad hoc classes or seminars, or other functions. For more information about booking the Hamilton Campus for an event please contact the Facilities Officer at x3655.</span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span lang="EN" style="font-family:<br />
&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN">Main telephone:&nbsp;905 547 3555</span></strong><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes"><br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">1842 King Street East<br />                      Hamilton, Ontario<br />                      L8K 1V7</span></span></p>
<p></p>
<p style="text-indent:0cm;tab-stops:list 36.0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
      </div>
